It is a behind-the-scenes look at how the engine is being built.


Engine Architecture
KSE is structured into three major layers:

1. Editor Layer
Tools for game creation:

Scene editor
Asset browser
Inspector panels
Scripting tools
UI panels and docking
2. Engine Layer
Core systems:

Renderer
ECS
Physics
Audio
Platform abstraction
Third-party libraries
3. Application Layer
Runtime components:

Game executable
Assets
Build output
Platform-specific deployment